comment:
*

* A table that stores the mappings between the image and the URL. *

*

* Deleting or Updating a mapping might also deletes the mapped image if there is no other URL * maps onto it. *

variables.name: CONTENT_URI
variables.comment: * The content:// style URI for this table

variables.name: CONTENT_TYPE
variables.comment: * The MIME type of {@link #CONTENT_URI} providing a directory of image mappings.

variables.name: CONTENT_ITEM_TYPE
variables.comment: * The MIME type of a {@link #CONTENT_URI} of a single image mapping.
